The singer Polina Gagarin called helping to lose weight products
Russian singer Polina Gagarin named five products that helped her adjust the figure and subsequently not gain weight again.
The first one on the list was water.
The singer prefers to drink clean, ungassed water before each meal to numb the feeling of hunger and eat less.
Also, to maintain the consistency, vegetable salad, brown rice and seafood will be ideal.
Thanks to them, it is possible to make a balanced diet: in vegetables there is fiber, in rice there are complex carbohydrates, and seafood are a source of protein, useful vitamins and amino acids.
For the days of unloading, the singer selects apples.
Thanks to these products, Gagarin was able to get rid of 30 extra kilograms.
In addition, the singer switched to a small diet - eating often and slightly and excluded from the diet fat, sweet and caloric.
Gagarin does not eat fried food, baked goods, sausage products and other meat semi-finished products, writes kp.ru on July 26.
It has also replaced red meat with fish and seafood.
He prefers vegetables (except potatoes), whole grain cereals and a lot of greens.
Gagarina is also active in the gym, yoga and running.
Earlier, Russian singer Sergey Lazarev told how he was able to drop the excess weight collected during the period of self-isolation.
According to the artist, he adjusted the food and actively engaged in running.
